🛠️ Troubleshooting
❌ Cart not found

Clear localStorage cart UUID

Ensure CARTS table has data

❌ ORA-00001 duplicate key

Resync sequences:

SELECT MAX(CANDIDATE_ID) FROM CANDIDATES;
❌ Receipt status error

Fix constraint:

ALTER TABLE RECEIPTS DROP CONSTRAINT CHK_RECEIPTS_STATUS;

ALTER TABLE RECEIPTS ADD CONSTRAINT CHK_RECEIPTS_STATUS
CHECK (STATUS IN ('INITIATED','SUCCESS','PARTIALLY_APPLIED','FAILED'));
❌ Payment not applied

Check webhook logs

Validate signature

Confirm reference match

